FBIS3-10733 "drlat048_n_94008" FBIS-LAT-94-048 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Mar 1994 Chile One of Lautaro's `Most Dangerous' Members Arrested PY1103025594 Santiago Television Nacional de Chile Imagen Internacional in Spanish 0000 GMT 11 Mar 94 PY1103025594 Santiago Television Nacional de Chile Imagen Internacional Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Excerpts] Investigative Police on 9 March at noon finally arrested Rosa Ester Vargas, the original mujer metralleta [submachine gun woman], who is regarded as the most dangerous subversive in the Lautaro group. She was arrested in the country's southern section with two other people. She was transferred today to a Civilian Police post under strict security measures. [passage omitted] Vargas participated mainly in attacks on banks. Police reported her arrest to Special Judge (Arnoldo Ereise), who investigates the subversive group's actions. She will be placed at his disposal in 10 days.
